You can pull images from DockerHub as you'd normally expect. The syntax is generally the same as `docker pull`, but the meaning is changed from "pull an image into your local workspace" to "pull an image to be used as a new release of your application". For example, `deis create example-go && deis pull deis/example-go:latest` will create the app then pull the image from DockerHub, promoting it as the build image.

